## 1. Product Overview\
\
### 1.1 Purpose\
\
Build an interactive \'93Crash-to-Repair\'94 digital experience for Volkswagen Brand Day that:\
\
- Uses a realistic racing/crash simulator (BeamNG) to generate vehicle damage data.\
- Transforms crash telemetry into a repair estimate (parts, pricing).\
- Connects that estimate to the VW dealer network (simulated or real data).\
- Demonstrates VW\'92s and Object Edge\'92s capability to:\
  - Turn complex data into intuitive customer/dealer experiences.\
  - Build meaningful, data-driven products extremely quickly using AI-driven development.\
\
This is primarily a **marketing/technology demo**, not a production system, but it should be structured so it can evolve into solving real business problems (e.g., inventory optimization, connected-car crash flows).\
\
