## 5. Non-Functional Requirements\
\
### 5.1 Performance\
\
- Single race \uc0\u8594  telemetry \u8594  estimate pipeline should complete in **\u8804  3\'965 seconds** under demo conditions.\
- UI transitions must feel snappy; no multi-minute waits.\
\
### 5.2 Reliability & Resilience\
\
- Solution must be stable enough to run multiple demos during the event day:\
  - Handle at least **dozens of runs** without restart.\
- If telemetry extraction fails:\
  - Show a graceful error screen and allow a retry run.\
\
### 5.3 Security & Privacy\
\
- No sensitive PII required; if any emails/names are captured, they may be fake for demo.\
- Local-only deployment for event is acceptable; no need for public internet exposure.\
- If any cloud is used (GCP), secure with standard service credentials; no hard-coded secrets.\
\
### 5.4 Maintainability & Handover\
\
- Design for **support handoff** to Brazil-based team (e.g., Valmor, Rene) for event day:\
  - Clear setup script/process.\
  - Documentation for:\
    - Restarting services.\
    - Common failure modes and quick fixes.\
- Code should be navigable by another dev using AI code assistants with the existing docs.\
\
